      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，并行结构。我确认一下：Authorization Service返回的是user_id和status，然后Gateway用这个user_id同时去查Profiles和Orders？Orders那边的alt分支是304 Not Modified和200 OK两种情况对吧？",
