      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把五个participant都建好了，Client、Gateway D、Authorization Service A、User Profiles Service B、Orders Service C。第一笔是Client带Bearer token发GET /v1/state到Gateway D。然后Gateway同步调Authorization的GET /v1/auth，拿到user_id之后开par并行。",
